That part which until 1.4.1935 formed parts of the parishes of 
    Llangollen Rural and Llantysilio. See also Table 2, note (c).

Created 1894 from the rural part of the parish of Llangollen Traian. 
    See also Table 2, notes (c) and (d).

Abolished 1894 to become the separate parishes of Llangollen Urban 
    and, Llangollen Rural.

Created 1894 from the part of the parish of Llangollen Traian 
    in Llangollen Urban District. See also Table 2, note (d).
